  "title": "AmbiguousSceneInstanceError",
  "description": "Thrown when `unload(Target)` is called with `options.instance` omitted while more than one activation (active, retained, and/or preloaded) exists for `Target` — there is no priority order; the caller must specify which one via `{ instance: 'active' | 'retained' | 'preloaded' }`, or `{ instance: 'all' }` to discard every one.",
